values:
"No relationship is perfect, ever. There are always some ways you have to bend, to compromise, to give something in order to gain something greater."


"The love we have for each other is bigger than these small differences. And that's the key. It's like a big pie chart, and the love in a relationship has to be the biggest peice. Love can make up for a lot." or cant it?

well its Monday afternoon. I jus got home from school.. only had to go for a 1/2 hour today.. i slept aalright last night.. i had a really bad dream tho. I was in my car and i went to the gas station.. and jon was sleeping in the car.. but i forgot to put the car in park so when i got out it started rolling away and went into oncoming traffic and jon was killed. i looked it up on the dream website to see what it means...

"To dream about the death of your ex-boyfriend, suggests that you are lacking a certain aspect or quality that the loved one embodies. Ask yourself what makes this person special or what do you like about him. It is that very quality that you are lacking in your own relationship or circumstances. Alternatively, it indicates that whatever that person represents has no part in your own life."

soo ya i guess thats what that means. i have soo manny damn things going through my head and now im sick.. really sick.. i have 102 fever this morning when i woke up.. i didnt eat anything all day yesterday and havent today except a banana and didnt even eat all of it. Im weak.. i keep crying and im jus completely misserable! i know this is for the best.. i know it is.. but its jus so hard to except.. Sarah told me last night.. to go by what my heart tells me.. not what my brain tells me.. because if you think about it..when does your brain hurt? never.. your heart is always the one that has you crying. Im goin with what my heart is telling me. All those times i thought i would manage if he ever broke up with me.. well that was jus a freakin cop out because.. look at me.. i cant even except it.. this jus tells me that i really was in love with him.. and he meant the world to me..

*everything happens for a reason* there must be a reason for this.. hopefully?

welll im gonna go.. watch some tv.. then ggo babysit.. i wish i was a kid again.. so then my heart wouldnt feel this hurt! so until later.. i love you.. i hope we can work things out.. xoxo

-Hales

"Love is needing someone. Love is putting up with someone's bad qualities because they somehow complete you" --This Lullaby ((jus a few words to go by))

I spent years and all this time
thinking I was better off cuz you were mine
You always said it was your way or the highway
So I'm shiftin my life into drive
I'm getting out kissing the past good-bye
Like Toby said, "How do you like me now?"
This conversation has run dry
And I keep telling myself


ooooooo, ooooooo, ooooooo
There's more to me than you
ooooooo, ooooooo
Don't underestimate what I can do
Well I'm alright, it's okay
I know I'll make it through
Cuz there's more to me than you


I'm not saying I'm battered and bruised
but I might as well be with the words you used
I believe in myself, that makes me stronger
Things changed and so have I
I'm gonna make hay while the sun still shines
You can clip my wings, but I'm still gonna fly
I'm on my own and on my way
And I keep telling myself

ooooooo, ooooooo, ooooooo
There's more to me than you
ooooooo, ooooooo
Don't underestimate what I can do
Well I'm alright, it's okay
I know I'll make it through
Cuz there's more to me than you

"There was always something that meant more to you than me"
And I'm just sorry it's taking this for you to see

ooooooooo, ooooooo, oooooo
There's more to me than you


There's more to me than you

well i dont think this day or this weekend could have gotten any worse. i hate everything about me right now. I ruined our relationship that i loved. All because im an "emotional rollercoaster" i have problems yes i know. But you were the only one who really understood me.. you knew that i had my problems. but you dealt with them. Im sorry for all the nagging i did to you.. i never thought that it would destroy our relationship. if i could iwould take it all back and start over new.. but i cant. I know you deserve someone who accepts you for who you are.. someone who can make you happy and who isnt so "stressful.. and i thought i was improving on the nagging and the stressfulness.. i thought that i was trying harder to make you happy.. because thats all i ever wanted was for you to be happy... and if your not happy in this relationship with me.. then i understand. you are my best friend.. my only friend practically.. your the reason i am who i am today. i thank you for putting up with me for as long as you did.. I jus want you to know that i love you and you mean more then the world to me.. no words can describe my feelings for you.. if "we" are meant to be then we will be & if its not then we'll kno that to. i love you hunnie baby! : )

ps. you better still be going with me to my prom.. because you already said you would : )...

Oh the first time that we ever danced together
You kissed me and I froze right where I stood
It felt just like that night could go on forever
That's the very moment my heart thought you would
Always Be, Always Be Mine
Always Be, Always Be Mine

Remember when we drove all night down to Daytona
I don't even think we ever saw the beach
We spent half our weeks vacation in a hotel room
And that might not be your favorite memory
But it will Always Be, Always Be Mine
Always Be, Always Be Mine

Oh I know you said we don't belong together
But if by chance you ever change your mind
And you need two arms still dying to hold you
It will always Be, Always Be Mine

I still keep your picture hanging in my bedroom
And all the letters in the bottom of the drawer
I still believe for every one there's only one true love
And I realize that I'll never be yours
But you'll Always Be, Always Be Mine
Always Be, Always Be Mine
Yes you'll Always Be, Always Be Mine
Always Be, Always Be Mine

yo yo yo... its Tuesday. Just got home from schoooly. I actually stayed the whole damn day. HA.. im proud of myself. I have to stay now because if i dont pass English 4 then i dont graduate. and i have to be there to pass. So now i HAVE to go! : ).. o well.. its ok. Anyways.. Last night i went over to James for a little while. Mainly sat in Taylor's room and we talked. James wasnt there. He was out. He turns 21 today! : )... now he can buy me annyyy alcohol i want.. hehe! There havin a little somethin tonight. Too bad i cant go... then Taylor's birthday is next week. Tuesday.. she turns 18! So there havin a party for the both of them Saturday.. ill deffinately be thurrr!!!! YAY... well after me and Taylor talked.. we all decided to go to Porky's for dinner. That sucked because our waitress sucked ass.. the food was damn good.. but she sucked! So we left absolutely NO tip. HA. then went back to James and came home around 8:30.. washed my face and went to sleepy sleepy. Woke up went to school. and now im jus sittin here waiting to get my ACT scores back. : ) ... im nervous!!!! i hope i did good.. mannn.. i realllly hope i did! Anyhoo.. i have to work today @ 4:00! bummer.. and i have to work tomorrow @ 4:00.. i got some new clothes for work tho.. soo im excited about that. what else is goin on. OH exactly ONE month till i turn 18.. thats 31 days babbbyyy! woo hoo.. im thinkin about goin somewhere.. like maybe to Georgia to hang with my girl Sarah. but i dont know yet.. we'll see when that time comes. alright well im gonna go watch my SOAPS... until later..

PEACE OUT MOTHA!

-Hales-

wellll today is Monday. No school for me! Since its Presidents Day. I slept until 11:30 and then woke up and jus been hangin out around the house. Im in a real lazy mood. Havent got to jus hang out in a LoOng time. But now i get too! I have to work everyday this week. Well except for Thursday and Saturday. This weekend, hasnt really been the Best. Me and Jonny are on a "break" since like Tuesday of last week. I think. I jus got soo upset about everything and i jus cant take it anymore. So i told him we needed to be on a break. I havent really been treating it as one. But i think i should start... like TODAY. Were DEFFINATELY not hangin out tonight. Hes goin to the movies with his "friends" from work. Soooo im thinkin about goin over to James' house. SInce i havent been over there in FOREVER.. all because of Jon. So that sounds like a plan. And if not then im jus gonna hang out here. I have got to Put my foot DOWN about this shit mann.. its jus soo damn hard to. Im not gonna go over there.. anymore.. maybe like once a week.. but thats IT! im done. seriously. He has got to realize that im serious about it. soo yea.. thats what im gonna do.

So anyways... I still havent heard from UWF. Im gettin kinda nervous now. I hope i get accepted. If not then its cool. Ill jus have to go to Edison for 2 years and then go to a different university. maybe thats whats best huh? My birthday is in a month tomorrow! Ill be 18. Can NOT waiittt!!!! Ill be legal.. hehe. : ). Well.. im gonna get goin.. go watch my Soaps. "Passions" best ever! So until later.. LOVE YOU!!!

hey hey.. i havent updated in a while.. soo much stuff has been goin on. Yesterday was Valentine's Day.. and once again it SUCKED.. i hate that day with a freakin passion.. it jus makes you so depressed. I thought it would be different if you had a boyfriend.. but i havent yet seen the difference. Jon didnt get me ONE thing. : (.. he never has.. ive never gotten one card... homemade or anything.. not one flower.. even if it was picked outa someones yard.. NOTHING.. and i thought it would be different since ya kno it is VALENTINES DAY.. the LOVE DAY!.. But thats a negative.. i even called him while he was at work and he totally cut me off to say "I cant talk right now.. im working" well whatever mannn... godd.. i hate relationships. I cried myself to sleep last night.. because its not fair.. its hurtful.. he says he loves me so much well then why doesnt he show me he does??? i mean i DEFFINATELY do not care about the material things (obviously not.. ive been with him for 10 months) but every once in a while it would be nice to actually get something from the person you love.. I made him a brownie and decorated it.. i made choc. covered strawberrries. i gave him 2 cards and a rose. I jus dont get it. i beginning to think that a women deserves better then that.. i mean i should deserve better then that. but i try to jus ignore it because i love him but really its hard when its a holiday. Am i over-reacting??? AND on top of all that... We keep fighting CONSTANTLY! geeshhh

Anyways.. work is goin alright.. i HATE working tho.. i mean i dont hate the job i jus hate goin there to work.. it sucks. School is goin good.. i got my report card..1 A, 2 B'S, & a C.  I applied to some colleges in Pensacola.. i thinks thats my only way outa here.. is to go to college. Ill end up goin there no matter what.. even if it is to a Junior college.

Im buying a dogg! a Maltipoo!!! omgoshh soo freakin cute. i love it. I cant wait till i can get it. Im gonna name it Mayzie.. i think.. i havent decided yet. But imma gettin it!!! Ill post pictures when i do. My birthday is in a month.. ill be turning 18! i wanna go on a vacation somewhere.. get a way for a while. so we'll see.

alright well ive written ENOUGH. until later.. peace out hommiee

well well well... its Friday night and i jus got home from work. HA work is soo freakin easy!!! Hostessing there is the absolute BEST. I do nothing.. except show people there tables then freakin leave & get paid $10 dollars an hour for doin it. So im happy with that dude. i get out early too. Mainly cus we dont serve late and we only take reservations. Jon moves into his house in a week. YAY.. im excited. I think hes supposed to spend the night tonight. Hes gonna call me around 9:30 i think um so maybe. HA.. i hope he can spend the night and doesnt have to work in the morning.. ive never gotten to sleep in with him at my house because he always used to sleep over during the week and id have to go to school the next morning. I wanna do something fun tomorrow tho. I didnt get paid today. i thought i would but i deffinately DONT.. so now i have to wait another 2 weeks to get it. :( ... osa wellsa. what else is new? Im plannin something EXTRA special for Valentines Day! i can not wait. Im sooooo excited. it should be a special evening for me and him! i wish i could give ya details but its a SURPRISE!!!! soo ill let you know after it happens how it went. alright well theres nothing else really to write about sooo until later.. 
i love you jonny..
xoxox- Hals

well things i guess are kinda lookin up.  I got my schedule for work.. there moving me to Hostess! i work Wed at 4 and then Friday at 4. only 2 days this week.. which is pretty shitty.. but ill get more.. therejus trainin me to be one. ill at least work 4-5 days in one week. Jons moves down today. well not totally.. but he starts workin here tomorrow morning. im happy about that. but im not happy with who hes gonna be stayin with.. but im gonna have to except it until they move into there house. (gotta make sacrifices right?) sooooo i get to see him tonigt! yAy... he doesnt seem to into seeing me tho. o well.. maybe im jus worried. i dont kno what it is. o welll... tomorrow we have NO schooL! yippppie!!! well alright my hair color is in my hair and i think its about time i washed it out.. before it turns colors on me! soooo ill update later!! until then... GOOD BYEEE!!!

everything is so wrong right now. im jus sooo depressed. i cant seem to jus put a smile on my face about anything.. school is goin good. im keeping my grades up but other then that nothings doin good. my relationship with my boyfriend isnt doin to well.. i feel like were on totally difeerent levels and i dont even kno him anymore. its like whenever we talk.. we have nothing to talk about.. or one way or another i start to cry. i dont kno whats goin on in my head. i dont know why this is happening to me.. and why we keep fighting. i wish it would all jus stop.. because i dont wanna cry anymore. i love him more then anything and i hate fighting with him.. thats why i never tell him how i feel.. because im afraid that if i do.. were jus gonna end up fighting about it.. because so far thats whats happened. everyone says that im afraid to hide my feelings well... i wonder why. nothing ever comes out good when i tell people how i feel. thats why im afraid to. so thats why i hide my feelings.. i wish people would understand me.. they say they do.. but they dont ever understand how i feel. what goes on in my brain.. its unexplainable. i jus wish me and jon can work things out.. i hate it when hes mad at me. i cant stand that feeling. if you read this jon.. im sorry about everything thats happened with us this past week. i wish you could jus understand me like you say you do.

anyways.. i work at 4.. till like i dont know. this job isnt me at all.. im not enjoyin being a server.. i mea i have fun.. but i dont think i wanna do it.. jus yet. i work tomorrow too at 4. he makes the schedule Sunday.. he better not work me everyday. 

well i dont think ineed to complain anymore. soo im gonna stop.

with love always..
Haley

my emotions are allll messed up mann. Im nervous about work today.. first day.. and im afraid of all the worst possible things.. i jus cant get them outa my mind mann.. this freakin sucks.. i work Tues, Wed, Thurs, Fri and Sat! can you believe that?? i deffinately can NOT! Jon hasnt called me or contacted me in the past 48 hours! which is reallllly pissin me off. and i kno if i call him he'll have some excuse to why he hasnt called me.. and i dont want another damn excuse... soo therefore im not callin him. he has to call me.. and if he doesnt well i guess we wont be talkin. (but then a part of me is worried about him.. but its not like hes never done this before.. because he HAS!.. this is nothing new.. it jus pisses me off that he still does it) but anyways... its 1:38.. i go into work at 3:00 till who knows when.. prob 10 or something weird like that. hopefully i dont work that long! but i probably will. i wouldnt be so afraid if i was hosting or something.. but im serving.. its driving me crazy that ive never done it before.. and now im becoming one. ahhh!!! and i dont even know what to wear! i kno black pants.. but i have no idea what shirt to wear.. or how im supposed to wear my hair.. that dumb dude never told me any of that! geeesshh!!.. plus im majorly tired and i wanna take a nap but i cant because then ill be even more tired by the time i have to get up and leave. gosh im complaining alot.. sorry... i gotta get it all out! alright well i gotta go worry some more.. and hope that jon can pick up his freakin phone and call!.. soo until then. im out.. love ya!

welll i start my new job tomorrow at 3:00! ahh im sooo scared. Im a server at Forest Glen Country Club. Ive never served before in my life.. and im afraid im gonna mess up or something. but i have to do it.. they pay realllly good and i have to pay my mom back. im feel so guilty for takin all her money all the time.. so hopefully i can handle being a server.. im kind of a ditz when it comes to that stuff. but im gonna put my working face on and do the best i can! 
school was alright today. it was boring and long like always.. and i was dead tired.. but i got through it. im mad at jon.. he doesnt kno it though.. he makes me so mad.. i havent 'talked' to him in 2 days.. like heard his voice.. WHY? o because HE HASNT CALLED! i hate when he does this shit.. and i deffinately am NOT calling him.. i feel like i always call him and he NEVER calls me.. sooo he better call me soon.. or i will not jus be pissed i will be ROYALLY PISSED... and then i jus wont talk to him.. i mean what is he possibly doin that he cant take 5 mins to call me and tell me he loves me or that hes FINE... UGHHHH! i hate guys.. especially when they pull shit like this. but whatever.. we'll see how long it takes him to call.

this week nothing going on. i have a wedding to go to Saturday, but i dont kno if i wanna go.. ill probably have to work or something. since i dont kno my schedule.. i cant make any plans. o well. well alright.. ive updated ENOUGH. 
love yall..
-H

yo yo yo! wow its been a while since i last wrote. i wrote on christmas and its already the last day of my winter break.. mannnn time flies! welllll Sarah came down on Monday.. and we had a lotta fun! She jus left yesterday. we went shoppin and we went outt.. and we went tot he beach. Good times mannn. anyywayss.. jon comes down Thursday.. ahhhh i miss him soooo freakin much! im crazy about that kid.. todays our 10 month anniversary. 10 months mann.. it feels weird. ive been with him that long.. it doesnt feel like it. time jus flies when your in love. I could NOT see my self with Any one else.. but him. you kno your in love with someone when alll you think about is him. and what i said before about me being worried with him up there.. im not anymore.. because i jus know that he loves me and he would never do anything to hurt me no matter what the circumstances are. so i cant wait to see him.. i jus wanna kiss him, hug him, hold him.. have sex with him! ahah.. i cant waittt. im sooo excited! ok i gotta stop talkin about him.. its drivin me crazy jus thinkin about it.
anyhoo.. i go back to damn school tomorrow.. this sucks.. but its my last semester of my high school career. wow..if you think about it like that its kind of weird. ahh and i turn 18. this should be a good end of the school year. i jus need to start applyin to colleges and get outa here. i wish i could go somewhere near jon. i want my own apartment. and i think im jus gonna have to go to a community college. which sucks but thats what happens when you get bad grades and you dont study for SATs o welll... alright well i gotta go to Wal Mart.. soo until later
i love you jonny & i misss you soooooooooo much! xoxoxxo
love
-H

Merry Christmas! yes today is Christmas.. it surely does NOT feel like it.. cus outside its hotter then ball sacks! but other then thats its been a good christmas.. I didnt get everything i wanted but thats jus fine.. it doesnt matter.. i got plenty. From my dad i got $100 dollars to the mall, a calendar, a picture frame, Victoria Secret pj's, Curious by Britney Spears, a Pedicure and Manicure kit, 2 shirts, and a bracelet. Then we ate dinner.. lobster and steak.. YUMMY. So then we came here and woke up and opened presents from my momma. i got a purse with a H on it, Curious.. (yes again), a Guess watch, hair straightner, a cd, love spell with a purse, and a bunch of stockin stuffers. Now were jus makin dinner.. and the familys comin over later to eat. Tomorrows my mommas birthday. and then Monday im goin to Orlando with James.. to pick up SaRah!!!.. cannt wait. 
 Anyways.. Jons in Michigan with his family for Christmas.. i miss him so much.. im thinkin about him constantly! and its drivin me crazy. he jus pops in my mind. no matter what it is im doin. I think its because hes up ther and i have no idea what hes doina nd it scares me. im worried.. but im tryin not to be.. i trust him! He comes back Jan 5th. the day i go back to school. : (.. i wish he would of came home earlier soo i can at least spend some of my break with him. but he cant. O well.. whatever.. but im gonna goo... until later.. 
i love you jon..
cant wait to see you Sarah!! gonna get CRUNK! HA
Love - H

yo yo! welll im at jons house in Sarasota! hes at work right now.. he has to work everynight 10-6 which blows! were about to drink some wine.. and have desert and then im gonna go visit jon and then go to bed.. cus i amm soo tired! its freaki ncold outside too mann.. we jus got done eating dinner at this nice restaurant.. jon had to wear a tie and i had to wear dressy clotes the food was alright really expensive tho. but anyways not to much else is goin on.. jus thought id catch ya up.. well im out.. laa ya! xox

welll im sitting here at my dads doin laundry right about now. Its Firday mornin.. and i dont have school anymore.. its Christmas Break! thank god... but of course i couldnt sleep in this mornin because i had to take Stuart and my brother to school. So that blew.. but other then that everythings fine.. i really wanna take a nap.. but ive got WAYYY to much stufff to do today!... im leavin to go to Sarasota.. i come back Monday. I hvave to clean all my clothes at my dads house since our washing machine is BROKEN! can you beleive that mann?? and then im goin home.. cleanin my room.. packin.. then gettin dressed and leavin. soooo i dont kno what time i should be gettin there,... but jons worried its goin to be late.. because he has to work every night.. 10-6.. while im there.. soo that sucks... but when i get there i get there.. im not gonna rush. School is over.. i got an A on my early childhood final.. an A on my Government and an F on my Economics Final!!! soooo that sucked.. but i still passed. I got my present from Rachel.. she got me the cutest stuff.. this pink purse with a butterfly on it.. and pink shirt soooooo cute! and then a necklace with a cross and a bracelet!!! from Deirdre i got a CD.. Mercy Me.. I can only imagine.. since someone stole it from me! soo that was good.. Dustyns makin a me a braclet... i cant wait till hes finished.. i wonder what its goin to say! anyways.. the things i got for jon are alright.. this onee thing thats like the best thing.. didnt come i yesterday sooooo i have to wait until i see him after he gets back from Detroit to give it to him.. which blows.. but o well.  i colored my hair yesterday.. because we have a family picture when i get back from Sarasota that Tuesday on the beach.. soo i have to look good. its goin to be freeezing Tuesday night too.. like the coldest day on the year.. thats jus great! but my hair looks good.. i think its kinda red.. because i let it sit and the i went to turn the water on to rinse it out and the water wasnt working soooooo i had to wait even longer for my brother to fix it.. i was getttin kinda scured! but everythings fine. well alright i better go finish the laundry.. then head home... ill write more later.. sarah ill call you this weekend.. or call me.. ill have my sisters cell.. ill tell you the number in an email.. i love you.. be good and safe this weekend! byee all! xoxoxox

wow.. livejournal is messin up mann. I finally can write an entry. welll my car is a TOTAL peice of shit! i hate that thing mann.. my air doesnt work to well anymore.. my tires need to be balanced.. my oil changed.. my speaker is blown.. NOW today.. i go to turn it off and it wouldnt shut off!!! its still runnin as we speak. i swear.. im soo mad. My dad is coming over today to look at it and see where we need to take it. Its about damn time.. i say the only place it needs to go is the damn dump! i mean what the hell kinda car wont turn off. Im supposed to go see Jon Friday sooo hopefully my dad will fix it by then. and if not i dont know what to do.. anyways.. its really cold out. this mornin i like froze to death in my car. ((since my heater doesnt work)) soo then at school 2nd block like literally sucked! the kids were wayy outa control and now that the teachers dont like me.. it sucks even more.. i jus feel like there always talkin about me. HA i dont care.. only 3 days left for me.. then im OUT! sooo it shouldnt be that bad.. i have finals Wed and Thurs. Im passing alllllllll my classed with 3 As and one freakin B. I cant wait tilll this term is done and over with. I went shopping yesterday with my momma. I got a lotta presents for my friends...!!! i cant wait to give them out! well alright theres not much else to say.. so until later... peace outtt!!!!

last time i updated was exactly one week ago from today. im sorry.. i promise ill start updating more.. jus never really feel like it. Well since the last time i wrote.. Jon came down for 3 days! Wed. Thu. and Fri. Then he left : (. I had fun tho!! Im goin up there Dec 17th for Christmas and then comin down here Dec 20th. Sarah is comin down!!! i really hope she can.. she still has to find a way to get somewhere closer so i can pick her up.  Hopefully shes here for New Years.. i havent seen her in forever.. and i would like to have fun that ngiht. Im doin a project right now for Economics. Its extra credit.. soo i better do it! My momma comes home today... shes been gone since Friday. I babysat last night.. i got paid 70 dollars! then i babysit Wednesday, Friday night, Saturday mornin and Sat night.. so my weekends pretty much filled up.. HAHA im sucha loser!!! o well i dont care.. its money that i need badly!!!!!! im gonna go running tonight.. after i get done with this project.. and then gonna come home and go to bed early.. i keep goin to bed LATE.. i need to quit that shit. anyhoo.. i gotta get goin.. finish my homework! Sarah i love you and be strong.. your gonna get through this.. Jon i love you.. even tho you wont get online right now to talk to me! whatever... but until later! LAAAA YAAAA!!! xoxxo

Haley spins tunes as
DJ Penetrating Jail Bait

Get your dj name @ Quiz Me

Jon is my
pretty crush

Get your sweetheart's pet name @ Quiz Me

today is Monday. A start to a new week. : (.. today i didnt really do much.. i went to school.. freakin sucked ass.. and of course me and rachel did NOT wanna go to 3rd block soooo we skipped and went to Maggie Moos! i love that place mann. Then i took her back to school and i went home. I cleaned my room.. cleaned the carpet.. cleaned the laundry room and then cleaned the kitchen. Ya.. after that i jus sat around and watched the television. DB was supposed to come over to give me my damn SAT book.. but of course he hasnt yet! i swear im gonna kill him. I have SAT's this Saturday and i havent even opened a book to study. i really hate myself right now.. because i have to do good on it. and i have a feeling im not goin to. so this sucks major balls because that tells me right there if i can get into a good college or not! but whatever. im not gonna stress about it. Tomorrow is our first home basketball game.. EVER! soo that should be exciting and then Jon comes down Wed morning and hes stayin with me till Friday!!! woo hooo! My mom is goin out of town this weekend.. i think she leaves Sat and comes back Monday. I dont know. She hasnt talked to me about it yet.. but i kno my sister isnt goin soo now i have to deal with her gay ass. : /.. sucky! whatever.. not much else to say... so Im OUT! 
*HOLLER*
<3 always- Haley Elizabeth

**HAPPY THANKSGIVING** yes i know i havent written in what seems like forever.. but i jus havent felt like writing in this thing. soo i write everynow and again.. and today im jus straight up bored soo i might as well do something. well since the last time i wrote i told you about how me and jon were doin a lot better.. and we still are. everything seems to be goin jus great. He was down Sat & Sun. we went to breakfast and dinner Sat and then Sun went to the Nascar race in Miami. that was a lotta fun. we had a good time. : ). Then we got home at like 11:30 and Jon left at like 4 in the morning to go back home. : (. It was good to spend some time with him. SO then Monday i went to school.. [[soo freakin tired!]] came home and slept all damn day. then Tuesday.. did nothin again. then Wed.. went to school.. came home and chilled.. my brother came into town from Tenn.. thats where he goes to college. so weve all been jus chillin. : ). 
I dont talk to Dustyn AT ALL! i really dont like him. hes a freakin weirdo. His brain is all messed up. I dont kno whats up with him. Stuart and i are on better terms now. even tho hes playin 2 girls.. which im really pissed about.. but im jus stayin out of it.. they'll find out sooner or later.. and they'll both hate him. o well! Still dont have a job : / o well.
